text: Sepiella is a genus of cuttlefish encompassing around seven species. ==Classification== *Genus Sepiella **Sepiella cyanea **Sepiella inermis, Spineless cuttlefish **Sepiella japonica, Japanese spineless cuttlefish **Sepiella mangkangunga **Sepiella ocellata **Sepiella ornata, Ornate cuttlefish **Sepiella weberi ==External links== Category:Cuttlefish Category:Cephalopod genera
title: Sepiella
